# Experimental agentic E2E checks (non-blocking)

This repo may use an **experimental** agentic E2E system (separate from the legacy `html/e2e/**` suite).

## Rule (guardrail)

- Treat agentic E2E as **signal-only** unless your team makes it gating.
- Do not modify the E2E suite codebase as part of Magento work unless explicitly requested.
- Do not assume org/site/persona defaults; read `DEVELOPMENT-LOCAL.md` and/or ask the developer.

## Runbook

See `agentic-e2e-runbook` skill.
